Title: 'Never give up '
DateModified: '2019-02-18'
DatePublished: '2019-02-18'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/never-give-up
SetInCountry: Usa
Category: I didn't expect to find
AuthorName: Judyann  Ferron
AuthorCountry: United States of America
Text: "Long ago in Jerusalem their was a man by the name have Benjamin he live with\
  \ his wife and his two children by the name of amzera and amera\nAmera is 7 years\
  \ old and amzera is 10 one day Benjamin wife decided to go camping for one week\
  \ alone and never return back home 4 weeks has passed and there are no sign of Benjamin\
  \ wife amzera and amera cry for one week straight and did not eat \nAmera started\
  \ getting sick and Benjamin rush her to the emergency room where she was pronounced\
  \ death from hearth attack and kidney failure Benjamin started feeling depress because\
  \ he still haven\u2019t seen his wife and he lost of of his children he prayed for\
  \ 40 days and 40 nights and he also fast for 40 days and 40 night \nOne week later\
  \ he lost his next daughter amzera from a car accident and he decided he wasn\u2019\
  t going to live any more he\u2019s gonna commit suicide while gathering the rope\
  \ and other stuff to commit suicide he heard a voice saying Benjamin never give\
  \ up no matter what fight until you can\u2019t fight any more but never give up\
  \ \nSuddenly Benjamin started praying and crying and asking GOD for the courage\
  \ to carry on with his life two years later Benjamin has founded his self a new\
  \ wife by the name of sarah and Sarah was pregnant for Benjamin and they live happily\
  \ ever after"
